reviewText:
Of course I do not hate it as named on the first star! I am just disappointed that my computer's blu-ray drive can read all BR discs I have in hand but it cannot find anything in the discs I received!
Unfortunately I could test them six months later after they arrived.
One of the best seasons on Television ever. Holds up on repeat watching.

The item was received damaged. Both discs had the cover paper torn. Also they plastic was cracked on the inside.
Just found out, the discs are scratched in places and will not play.
I'm sending it back for a refund.
Love this show, glad I could get both seasons together.
The item was in good condition and was exactly as described. This show is amazing and the bundle made it a lot cheaper than buying separate!
